<h2>Discord Moderator</h2>
<p class="subtitle">Discord moderator plays a crucial role in maintaining order, safety, and a positive atmosphere on the server. Their main tasks include monitoring chat and channels, removing inappropriate content, and responding to violations of community guidelines.</p>
<p class="recruitment">Recruitment: Open</p>
