<p></p>

<p>
<span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color: #00c0ff;"><strong>Discord Moderator</strong></span><span style="color: #ffca00;"> - Who is that?</span></span>
</p>

<p>
<span style="background-color:transparent; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:13px;"><span style="font-size:14px">Discord Moderator is a person responsible for maintaining order and safety on a Discord server. They have the authority to manage members, moderate the chat, and make decisions regarding the server rules. Their main tasks include answering questions, moderating messages, resolving player issues, and ensuring that the server rules are not violated.</span></span>


</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="background-color:transparent"><strong><span style="color: #ff4545;font-weight: bold;font-family: arial;">Requirements:</span> </strong></span></span></p>

                        <ul>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">Daily activity on the CyberTankz server.
</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">Familiarity with and understanding of the rules applicable on the server.

</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">Experience in moderating other Discord servers.

</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">Knowledge of Discord features, such as managing roles, channels, and permissions.

</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">Communication skills.

</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">Ability to maintain discretion regarding privacy matters; confidential information must not be disclosed.
</span></li><li><span style="font-size:14px">Proficiency in effectively resolving conflicts.
</span></li><li><span style="font-size:14px">Commitment.


</span></li></ul>
<p style="margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; text-align:left"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="background-color:transparent"><strong><span style="color: #4bb929;">Benefits:</span></strong></span></span><br>
</p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">You will receive compensation in the form of crystals for the work done.
</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">You will get Microchip paint.
</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">You have a chance to become the Helper of the Month.
</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">You will receive early information about game updates.
</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:14px">You will have the opportunity to meet new people.
</span></li>
</ul>
